abstract: Former New York Jets linebacker Jermaine Cunningham, who is accused of distributing racy photos of woman, unlawful weapons transport and possession of hollow-point bullets, is barred from pretrial diversion program that would allow any conviction to be wiped from his record.
lead_paragraph: The linebacker Jermaine Cunningham, a Jet last year, cannot enter a pretrial diversion program that would allow any conviction to be wiped from his record.

headline.main: Ex-Jet Is Barred From Pretrial Program
headline.print_headline: Ex-Jet Is Barred From Pretrial Program
